<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
Get the wizard.<BR>Get the best telamon pet.<P>1) Go to aquaduct gobs.<BR>2) Send pet to a gob in the middle but not tangler.<BR>3) When they are close enough to your pet, mez or root them all.<BR>4) Proceed to kill them all by nuking the ones your telamon attacks. Have the wizard do the same.<BR>5) It takes practice, but control your telamon to NOT attack the tangler until its close to being the last one left.<BR>(Killling tangler quickly results in camp pop.)<BR>6) If you feel mez wearing off, cast root. <P>P.S. Before you start these instructions, kill the scout gobs first.<P>Good luck.
</FONT>
