<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I DO have the tela attack the tangler first.  Hit him once, then go passive & have the group chase toward the coast.  By pulling the group away, it gives you time to root/mez (& gets you safely away fomr the camp in case of repop) & by killing the tangler first, you wont have to wait for a respawn very often.<P>--------------------<P>Palomides / Alat-Seldi<BR>Mezmo - Level 50 Sorcerer<BR>Siege - Level 32 Armsman<BR>Tagalong - Level 20 Full-Enhance Cleric<BR>Miracle - Level 11 Full-Rejuv Cleric<BR>Recurve - Level 10 Scout<BR>Melodious - Level 1 Camelot Vaultkeeper
