<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I preferred to have someone group with me if only to make things more fun though solo may be fasster exp.<P>First try to get the highest telemon possible, the highest ones I got were 47 but I think they go up to 48. At 49 it becomes a breeze with medial telemon.<P>I would stand in the area northwest of the aqueduct away from the water (between aqueduct and road). It can be helpful to first dispatch the nearer goblin scout and his occasional buddy by standing in his range but not too close to the arches (helped to go near arch then walk backwards a bit, that way the scout and friend usually attack telemon instead of sorcerer).<P>Next, pull the tangler with level 8 amnesia at maximum range (sometimes takes a few casts). The instant the gobbies aggro, start walking backwards for about 7 to 10 steps (better to get as far away from arches as possible to avoid aggro from repops), then AE root them all, if any get past have tele attack them. Take a few more steps backwards and start nuking them down. After a couple die AE mezz the rest, this gives plenty of time to kill the whole pull.<P>It can help to have an /assist macro key set up to target the ones the telemon is attacking (though with 35 body I was able to nuke most down solo). <P>Use target objet - grab hotkeys to pick up the massive amount of bags  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">
</FONT>
