Did the aquaduct tanglers the other day with a scout and a cleric all of us 46. No Telamon. Scout shoots tangler, root, root, root till they're in a bunch, then ae mez. Scout pulls them one at a time, you nuke the one he pulls. Just as they get to you cleric stuns it to let the last few shots get in to kill it. Repeat as needed.<P>--------------------<P>Elbarad<BR>Percival<BR>Dux Bellorum
