Hi all,<P>first of all I found this forum some days ago and this is my first post. I have seen some very nice taktics that someone has discovered to do gobs solo and so on.<P>At the moment my Sorc is L44 with /played about 11 days or so. That is quite fast I think. I played in tangler gob partys from L37. There all gobs where red to me except some tanglers. So I could mezz dem quite effectiv with int/dex buff. I am mind spec at 44 and rest into body (L12 at the moment), so I have no AE root at the moment.<P>Of course if I had known some technics how to do gobs bevor I leveled up to L40 I would have spect body first to have ae root, but I can mezz handle them also if I don't have the root (of course it would be easier then).<P>So I play on Europe and we have still 1.45. That means I can't get a tela as pet I use peallaid because they are quit fast and go up Level 45.<P>I usually play with a cabba in my group, who sends in his pet, and let the pet die. He stands near the gobs so that the gobs go agro to him after that. This means all gobs run towards him in a very compact group that I can easy mezz with one cast. Maybe some single gobs add later but they are handled quite fast with some DDs. At the moment I have also a wizzard in my group because me and my cabba friend don't have good dmg with the baseline lifetrap and we need some sort of dmg dealer in the group to make it fast end effektiv. If I and my cabba reach L45 we get the last baseline lifetrap and we will start doing the gobs without a wizzard I think.<BR>Usually after we have cleaned out the aquaduct spot the cabba let his pet standing at the respawn place, so afther respawn the gobs go agro the golem immediately and we repeat...<P>--------------------<P>&#8364;XP&#8364;CT TH&#8364; UN&#8364;XP&#8364;CT&#8364;D<P>Beowolve
